reviewText: If you enjoyed "The Tall Blond Man With One Black Shoe,"  you are going to love this sequel.  This is one of the few times when a sequel surpasses the original.  Faster paced than the original and hilarious.  Even having to read the subtitles didn't detract from the fun.
If you saw the first movie "The tall blond man with one black shoes",and enjoy it,you 're not going to be desapointed with this one.
